quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  22,1,Yemwe bantu! Nimugandukire Nyagasani wanyu! Mu by’ukuri umutingito wo ku munsi w’imperuka ni ikintu gihambaye
  22,2,"Umunsi muzawubona, buri wese wonsa azibagirwa uwo yonsaga, ndetse na buri wese utwite azakuramo inda. Uzanabona abantu babaye abasinzi kandi atari bo (nta cyo banyoye), kubera ko ibihano bya Allah bizaba bikomeye"
  22,3,"No mu bantu hari abajya impaka kuri Allah nta bumenyi babifitiye, bakanakurikira buri shitani ryigometse"
  22,4,"(Iryo shitani) ryaciriweho iteka ko uzarigira inshuti rizamuyobya, rikazanamuganisha mu muriro ugurumana"
  22,5,"Yemwe bantu! Niba mushidikanya ko izuka rizabaho (nimutekereze uko twabaremye): Mu by’ukuri twabaremye tubakomoye mu gitaka (umukurambere wanyu Adamu), hanyuma (mwe tubarema) mu ntanga, hanyuma (zihinduka) urusoro rw’amaraso, hanyuma (zihinduka) ikinyama kigaragaza ishusho n’ikitayigaragaza; kugira ngo tubagaragarize (ubushobozi bwacu). Tunarekera muri nyababyeyi uwo dushaka kugeza ku gihe cyagenwe, maze tukabasohora (muri nyababyeyi) muri impinja, (tukabakuza) kugira ngo muzagere mu gihe cyanyu cy’ubukure. No muri mwe, hari abapfa batarageza icyo gihe (cy’ubukure), ndetse no muri mwe hari n’abagera mu zabukuru bakamera nk’aho batigeze bagira icyo bamenya. Ndetse ubona ubutaka bwumagaye, maze twabumanuraho amazi (imvura) bukanyeganyega bukanabyimba, bukanameraho ibimera binyuranye bishimishije"
  22,6,"Ibyo ni ibigaragaza ko Allah ari ukuri, kandi ko ari We uha ubuzima ibyapfuye, ndetse ko ari We ushobora byose"
  22,7,"Kandi ko imperuka izaza nta gushidikanya, ndetse ko Allah azazura abari mu mva"
  22,8,"No mu bantu hari ujya impaka ku byerekeye Allah nta bumenyi (abifitiye), nta muyoboro ndetse nta n’igitabo kimumurikira (afite)"
  22,9,"(Uwo muntu ujya impaka) anaga ijosi (agaragaza imyitwarire y’ubwibone) kugira ngo ayobye (abantu) inzira ya Allah; azagira ikimwaro ku isi, ndetse no ku munsi w’imperuka tuzamusogongeza ibihano by’umuriro utwika"
  22,10,"(Azabwirwa ati) “Ibyo ni ukubera ibyakozwe n’amaboko yawe, kandi mu by’ukuri Allah ntarenganya abagaragu be.”"
  22,11,"Ndetse no mu bantu hari ugaragira Allah ashidikanya. Iyo icyiza kimugezeho aratuza, naho yagerwaho n’ikigeragezo agasubira mu buhakanyi (nyuma y’uko yari yarayobotse); ubwo akaba ahombye (ibyiza byo ku) isi n’imperuka. Icyo ni cyo gihombo kigaragara"
  22,12,Asenga ibitari Allah bitagira icyo bimutwara cyangwa ngo bigire icyo bimumarira. Uko ni ko kuyoba guhambaye (kutagira igaruriro)
  22,13,"Asenga icyo inabi yacyo iri hafi kurusha ineza yacyo, kandi rwose (ibyo bihitiyemo kugaragira bitari Allah) ni byo barinzi babi ndetse bikaba n’inshuti mbi"
  22,14,"Mu by’ukuri ba bandi bemeye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza, Allah azabinjiza mu busitani butembamo imigezi (Ijuru), kuko rwose Allah akora ibyo ashaka"
  22,15,"Uwo ari we wese wibwira ko Allah atazatabara (Intumwa Muhamadi) kuri iyi si ndetse no ku munsi w’imperuka, namanike umugozi ku gisenge maze awushyire mu ijosi, narangiza awuce (yiyahure) maze arebe ko umugambi we (mubisha) ukuraho uburakari bwe"
  22,16,"Uko ni na ko twahishuye imirongo isobanutse (igitabo cya Qur’an), kandi Allah ayobora uwo ashaka"
  22,17,"Mu by’ukuri ba bandi bemeye (Allah n’intumwa ye Muhamadi), Abayahudi (abemeye ubutumwa bwa Musa ku gihe cye), Abaswaabi’i (abagumye kuri kamere yabo batagize idini bayoboka), Abanaswara [abemeye ubutumwa bwa Issa (Yesu) ku gihe cye], Abamajusi (abasenga umuriro) ndetse n’abasenga ibindi bitari Allah; rwose Allah azabakiranura ku munsi w’imperuka. Mu by’ukuri Allah ni Umuhamya uhebuje wa buri kintu"
  22,18,"Ese ntubona ko ibiri mu birere n’ibiri ku isi, izuba, ukwezi, inyenyeri, imisozi, ibiti, ibiremwa byose bigenda ku isi ndetse na benshi mu bantu byubamira Allah? Ariko abenshi (mu bantu batamwubamira) bakwiye ibihano. Kandi uwo Allah yasuzuguje ntawamwubahisha, kuko mu by’ukuri Allah akora ibyo ashaka"